{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2142552, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "举国体制≠有国家拨款", "timestamp": 1627352796, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142563, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142552, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那举国体制是啥", "timestamp": 1627352939, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142570, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大国都是举国体制啊，但是人家的选拔赛不像我们搞人情世故，就按成绩说话决定谁上", "timestamp": 1627353032, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142576, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142570, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我不信，我感觉人类都差不多😂", "timestamp": 1627353107, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142586, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142563, "tag": null, "text": "https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%BE%E5%9B%BD%E4%BD%93%E5%88%B6/6658482?fr=aladdin", "timestamp": 1627353137, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142594, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142563, "tag": null, "text": "举国体制是指以国家利益作为最高目标，国家体育管理机构在全国范围内调动相关资源和力量，国家负担经费来配置优秀的教练员和软硬件设施，集中选拔、培养、训练有天赋的优秀体育运动员参加奥运会等国际体育赛事，在比赛中与他国竞争，争取优异比赛成绩、打破记录、夺取金牌的体育体制。\n由政府选拔和培养有天赋的运动员参加比赛，这样做的最大的好处就在于可以集中力量，使优秀的教练员都有统一的观念和训练计划。在这种制度下，运动员守纪律，训练刻苦，求胜欲望非常强烈，这在奥运比赛中是致胜的关键。\n与举国体制相对应的是市场体制，指的是选拔和培养运动员的经费及其它费用由市场行为来筹集。", "timestamp": 1627353216, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142601, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142570, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 了解一下梦一队为什么没有伊塞亚托马斯", "timestamp": 1627353320, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142603, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142576, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 美国游泳不就是的，就一场定胜负，再有资历老将也得下，不会像体操这次选拔垫底的上", "timestamp": 1627353340, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142604, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142601, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 也是，但实力碾压赢了就没话说", "timestamp": 1627353389, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142607, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142594, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: ？你发的这个定义不就是以经费来源为区分标准的吗？", "timestamp": 1627353466, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142667, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142607, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 嗯，我错了😭", "timestamp": 1627353855, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142685, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142607, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那我重新阐述一下我的想法，我觉得每个国家的经费都有政府和市场两部分组成，但是比例不一样，因为我国职业化程度相对低，所以国家投入占比重很大，尤其是我们那些夺冠的优势项目，所以我们国家就被划入举国体制里了", "timestamp": 1627354014, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142752, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142685, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我们夺冠的那些项目在世界范围内职业化水平都很低吧？", "timestamp": 1627354632, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2142754, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142685, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 就挺怪的", "timestamp": 1627354641, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2143988, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 415579, "reply_to": 2142754, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果你把因果换一下或许就不奇怪了", "timestamp": 1627368221, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 415579, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "好奇，欧美几个大国的运动员不也是职业运动员吗？协会不也有国家拨款吗？为什么他们就不算举国体制呢？", "timestamp": 1627352630, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1627368221, "url": "", "vote": {}}}